Zhamel is a Rust implementation of the FreeBSD amd64 UEFI loader with feature
parity against loader.efi and additional ZFS unlock support.

The package installs the EFI binary under:

  /usr/local/share/efi/FreeBSD/zhamel.efi

Deploy it manually to the EFI system partition, typically as:

  /boot/efi/EFI/FreeBSD/loader.efi

WWW: https://github.com/hazayan/zhamel
